      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should check but i dont have my kit on me right now and im feeling way too dizzy to move much. i usually feel better once my levels stabilize. if i just take like 2 or 3 units of my rapid acting insulin, wouldn't that help prevent a massive spike from the post-workout stuff? i just want to get ahead of it so i dont feel even worse. what do u think?",
